{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859014173,"sessionID":"ses_2868fbefdffeeRYOnFfI3FPnHH","part":{"id":"prt_d79704bff001prt2sGBrfUj25M","messageID":"msg_d797042000015y2dZaE6kGi6MR","sessionID":"ses_2868fbefdffeeRYOnFfI3FPnHH","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_5312518948ad4ac7829fa1e9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the codebase at /home/dsj/benchmark to understand the \"agentcube project\" structure. Look for:\n1. Any files related to \"DockerService\" or \"docker_service\"\n2. Any AR (Archive/Architecture Record) files, especially AR-024\n3. The cmd/cli module structure\n4. Any Python files related to Docker service encapsulation\n5. Any CHANGELOG, ARCHIVE, or project documentation files\n\nSearch thoroughly using glob patterns like:\n- **/*docker*\n- **/*AR-024*\n- **/*archive*\n- **/cmd/cli/**\n- **/*.md\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of what you find, including file paths and their contents/purposes.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2868fa57cffes0bp63wlK0oxAn (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the AgentCube project structure and all requested findings.\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Summary: AgentCube Project\n\n### 1. Project Overview\n\nThe codebase at `/home/dsj/benchmark` is an **SDD Token Efficiency Evaluation (SDD-TEE)** framework that benchmarks AI coding assistants against the **AgentCube** open-source project (https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube). The AgentCube project is a sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents, built with Go (control plane) and Python (CLI, SDK, integrations).\n\nThe benchmark decomposes AgentCube into **43 fine-grained ARs (Architectural Requirements)**, each processed through a 7-stage SDD workflow (ST-0 through ST-7).\n\n---\n\n### 2. DockerService / docker_service Files\n\n**Primary source file:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` (221 lines)\n\nThis is a Python class `DockerService` that encapsulates the Docker SDK for Python (`docker>=6.0.0`). It provides:\n\n| Method | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `__init__(verbose)` | Stores verbose flag |\n| `check_docker_available()` | Pings Docker daemon, returns bool |\n| `build_image(...)` | Builds Docker image, returns metadata dict |\n| `get_image_info(image_name)` | Gets local image metadata (public) |\n| `_get_image_info(image_name)` | Internal helper for image metadata |\n| `_format_size(size_bytes)` | Formats bytes to human-readable string |\n| `push_image(...)` | Pushes image to registry with optional login/retag |\n| `_docker_login_sdk(...)` | Authenticates to Docker registry |\n| `_tag_image_sdk(...)` | Retags a local Docker image |\n| `remove_image(image_name)` | Removes a local Docker image |\n\n**Test file:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py` (424 lines)\n  - 31 test cases covering all methods\n  - All tests use `unittest.mock.patch` to mock `docker.from_env()`\n  - Tests organized into classes: `TestDockerServiceCheckDockerAvailableRunning`, `TestDockerServiceBuildImageSuccess`, `TestDockerServiceGetImageInfo`, `TestDockerServiceRemoveImage`, `TestDockerServicePushImageSpec`, `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Success`, etc.\n\n**Consumers of DockerService:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` -- calls `DockerService.build_image()`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` -- calls `DockerService.push_image()`, `check_docker_available()`, `_docker_login_sdk()`\n\n---\n\n### 3. AR-024 (DockerService Encapsulation) Files\n\nAR-024 is the **DockerService 封装** (DockerService Encapsulation) change request. It lives at:\n\n**Directory:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/`\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| `proposal.md` | 33 | Skeleton proposal (Module: cmd/cli, Language: Python, Size: M) |\n| `design.md` | 334 | Full technical design: architecture diagram, component design for all 8 methods, data flow (Build/Publish), error handling matrix, testing strategy, implementation notes |\n| `delta-spec.md` | 196 | 12 requirements, 23 GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering initialization, availability check, build, image info, size formatting, push, login, tagging, removal, verbose logging |\n| `tasks.md` | 176 | 9 atomic tasks (T1-T9) with dependency graph, parallelizable groups, and 9 acceptance criteria (AC1-AC9) |\n\n**Key tasks in tasks.md:**\n- T1: Fix `_docker_login_sdk` return type `bool` -> `None`\n- T2: Fix `_tag_image_sdk` return type `bool` -> `None`\n- T3: Implement `_get_image_info` internal helper\n- T4: Implement `get_image_info` public method\n- T5: Implement `remove_image`\n- T6: Fix `push_image` signature and implementation\n- T7: Update `PublishRuntime` caller\n- T8: Update existing test assertions\n- T9: Lint, type-check, coverage gate (>=90%)\n\n**Execution logs:** 7 stage logs exist at `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/`:\n- `AR-024_ST-0.log` through `AR-024_ST-6.log`\n\nThe implementation was completed with **31/31 tests passing** and **96% code coverage**.\n\n---\n\n### 4. cmd/cli Module Structure\n\n**Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/`\n\n```\ncmd/cli/\n├── pyproject.toml              # Package: agentcube v0.1.0, console script: kubectl-agentcube\n├── agentcube/\n│   ├── __init__.py             # Package version __version__\n│   ├── cli/\n│   │   └── main.py             # Typer app with pack/build/publish/invoke/status commands\n│   ├── models/\n│   │   └── pack_models.py      # MetadataOptions dataclass\n│   ├── operations/             # (additional operations module)\n│   ├── runtime/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py         # Re-exports runtimes\n│   │   ├── pack_runtime.py     # PackRuntime\n│   │   ├── build_runtime.py    # BuildRuntime (uses DockerService)\n│   │   ├── publish_runtime.py  # PublishRuntime (uses DockerService)\n│   │   ├── invoke_runtime.py   # InvokeRuntime\n│   │   └── status_runtime.py   # StatusRuntime\n│   └── services/\n│       ├── __init__.py         # Services package docstring\n│       ├── docker_service.py   # DockerService (221 lines)\n│       ├── metadata_service.py # AgentMetadata, MetadataService\n│       ├── k8s_provider.py     # KubernetesProvider\n│       └── agentcube_provider.py # AgentCubeProvider\n├── tests/\n│   ├── cli/\n│   │   ├── test_build_command.py\n│   │   ├── test_invoke_command.py\n│   │   └── test_status_command.py\n│   ├── runtime/\n│   │   ├── test_build_runtime.py\n│   │   ├── test_publish_runtime.py\n│   │   ├── test_invoke_runtime.py\n│   │   └── test_status_runtime.py\n│   ├── services/\n│   │   ├── test_docker_service.py      # 31 tests, 424 lines\n│   │   ├── test_k8s_provider.py\n│   │   ├── test_agentcube_provider.py\n│   │   └── test_metadata_service.py\n│   └── integration/\n│       ├── __init__.py\n│       └── test_build_e2e.py\n└── examples/\n```\n\n**Dependencies (from pyproject.toml):** typer, pydantic, pyyaml, httpx, docker>=6.0.0, rich, packaging, semver, kubernetes (optional)\n\n---\n\n### 5. Python Files Related to Docker Service Encapsulation\n\n| File | Path | Purpose |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `docker_service.py` | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Core DockerService class (221 lines) |\n| `test_docker_service.py` | `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py` | 31 unit tests (424 lines) |\n| `build_runtime.py` | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | Calls `DockerService.build_image()` |\n| `publish_runtime.py` | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Calls `DockerService.push_image()`, `_docker_login_sdk()` |\n| `__init__.py` | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Exports DockerService |\n\n---\n\n### 6. CHANGELOG, ARCHIVE, and Project Documentation Files\n\n**No CHANGELOG or ARCHIVE files exist** in the repository. The project uses an SDD (Spec-Driven Development) workflow with AR (Architecture Record) directories instead.\n\n**Key documentation files:**\n\n| File | Path | Purpose |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `README.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/README.md` | SDD-TEE framework overview, 5-dimension metrics, quick start |\n| `PLAN.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/PLAN.md` | AgentCube Implementation Plan mapping AR-023 through AR-033 to files (1441 lines) |\n| `proposal.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/proposal.md` | Top-level proposal |\n| `PROPOSAL.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/PROPOSAL.md` | Duplicate/alternate proposal |\n| `task.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/task.md` | Task definition |\n| `specs/project.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/project.md` | Project-level spec |\n| `cli-toolkit/design.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/.../cli-toolkit/design.md` | CLI toolkit design document |\n| `cli-toolkit/spec.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/.../cli-toolkit/spec.md` | CLI toolkit specification |\n| `SDD开发Token消耗度量指标体系设计方案.md` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/docs/SDD开发Token消耗度量指标体系设计方案.md` | Chinese-language SDD token metric design |\n\n**Spec documents (under `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/`):**\n- `sandbox-orchestration/` -- AR-005 sandbox creation processor\n- `cli-toolkit/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `code-execution/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `deployment/` -- design.md, spec.md, client-go.md\n- `ci-cd/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `python-sdk/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `session-store/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `session-routing/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `idle-cleanup/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `integrations/` -- design.md, spec.md\n- `testing/` -- agentcube_tdd_manifest.md\n\n**Change request archives:** 24 AR directories exist under `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/` (AR-001 through AR-024), each containing `proposal.md`, `design.md`, `delta-spec.md`, and `tasks.md`.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2868fa57cffes0bp63wlK0oxAn","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775858899584,"end":1775859014169}}}}
